uns and obtaining training resulted in an eight eight decrease in rape for that area the only city of its size in the country to experience a decrease of crime for that year additionally a one nine seven nine us justice department study of three two zero zero zero attempted rapes showed that overall when rape is attempted the completion rate is three six but when a woman defends herself with a gun the completion rate drops to three one g kleck point blank guns and violence in america aldine de gruyter ny one nine nine one two jd wright ph rossi armed and considered dangerous a survey of felons and their firearms aldine de gruyter ny one nine eight six unlike cats dogs never scratch you when you wash them they just become very sad and try to figure out what they did wrong dave barry seth eliot dept of material science and engineering carnegie mellon univerity pittsburgh pa arpa eliot cmu edu or se zero eight andrew cmu edu bitnet se zero eight andrew cmccvb